title: Buy a Boss Beauties NFT
body:
I propose that we buy a Boss Beauties NFT. It's one of the newer women-led women-focused PFP collections, and they recently announced a partnership with Marvel.  It is still under 1 ETH and would make an excellent investment for our vault.
